\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999995830504264, \"rank\": 2.0813327679374287e-07, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1440, \"end\": 1449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9138701793689434, \"rank\": 0.09401040582413654, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was their best dancer.\\\"\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But double gold-winning canoeistJess Foxwas among those to rush to Gunn's defence on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1548, \"end\": 1552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.8478601356739489, \"rank\": 0.17766247413852415, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is devastating for her,\\\" Fox told local media in Sydney.\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9999936570462691, \"rank\": 4.514938053331798e-06, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 1631, \"end\": 1637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999929958716802, \"rank\": 7.0